/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: MD_ORG */
/*==============================================================*/
create table MD_ORG
(
"OrgID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"OrgCode" VARCHAR2(50) not null,
"OrgName" NVARCHAR2(200) not null,
"OrgLevel" INTEGER not null,
"ParentID" INTEGER,
"OrderNum" INTEGER not null,
"StartTime" TIMESTAMP not null,
"EndTime" TIMESTAMP,
"Enable" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32) not null,
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP default SYSDATE not null,
"ModifyBy" NUMBER(32),
"ModifyTime" TIMESTAMP,
constraint PK_MD_ORG primary key ("OrgID")
);

comment on table MD_ORG is
'总部、大区、小区';

comment on column MD_ORG."OrgLevel" is
'1: 总部
2: 大区
3: 小区';

comment on column MD_ORG."OrderNum" is
'同级别组织内排序号';

comment on column MD_ORG."Enable" is
'1: 有效
0：无效';
